                    Current
                  </span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400"
                    >11/2024 – Present</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
              <ul
                class="space-y-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 list-disc list-inside"
