                  consistency, scalability, and accuracy while contributing to
                  system architecture and reliability within a microservice
                  ecosystem.</span
                >
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="relative z-10 flex-shrink-0">
              <div
                class="w-14 h-14 bg-white border rounded-full dark:bg-neutral-950 border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <img
                  src="/assets/images/experiences/inetum.webp"
                  alt="Inetum"
                  class="w-8 h-8"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <div
                class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-2 mb-3"
              >
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold dark:text-white">
                    Software Engineer
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
                    Inetum / Automotive Customer – Poland
                  </p>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400"
                  >10/2023 – 11/2024</span
                >
              </div>
              <ul
                class="space-y-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 list-disc list-inside"
              >
                <span
                  >Developed self-service platforms and backend services with
                  CQRS, Event Sourcing, and KSeF integration, enhancing
                  scalability, compliance, and system performance.</span
